 horizon kinetics account access contact paradigm fund wwnpx no load class overview the fund us focused allcap fund comprised of investments in misunderstood or underappreciated companies whose businesses exhibit long product life cycles and have substantial barriers to entry proprietary inhouse research sources original investment opportunities in companies for which investors fail to distinguish between permanent and transitory problems the strategy seeks to capture longterm results commensurate with the returns of companies’ underlying businesses and has low turnover paradigm fund commentary read more about the paradigm fund in this commentary paradigm fund fact sheet learn more about the paradigm fund in this fact sheet performance overview growth of  since inception the paradigm fund no load class inception date is   figures include changes in principal value reinvested dividends and capital gains distributions  performance data quoted represents past performance and does not guarantee future results  investment return and principal value will vary and shares may be worth more or less at redemption than at original purchase  the most recent monthend performance data is listed below or you may obtain it by calling us at   current performance may be lower or higher than the performance data quoted  performance data does not reflect the deduction of the sales load or fee which if reflected would reduce the performance quoted  you will be charged a redemption fee equal to  of the net amount of the redemption if you redeem or exchange your shares  days or less after you purchase them portfolio characteristics as of june   inception date december   net assets  million total holdings  turnover ratio  investment style global equity market cap focus all cap minimum purchase  portfolio managers murray stahl chairman chief executive officer chief investment officer cofounder murray is chief executive officer chairman of the board of horizon kinetics and is a cofounder of 