 also those that provide new kinds of services or products made possible by the development of the internet as well as existing businesses that are radically reinventing themselves through the internet such companies typically enjoy high barriers to entry such as proprietary content or technology that is difficult to replicate internet fund commentary read more about the internet fund in this commentary internet fund fact sheet learn more about the internet fund in this fact sheet performance overview growth of  since inception the internet fund no load class inception date is   figures include changes in principal value reinvested dividends and capital gains distributions  performance data quoted represents past performance and does not guarantee future results  investment return and principal value will vary and shares may be worth more or less at redemption than at original purchase  the most recent monthend performance data is listed below or you may obtain it by calling us at   current performance may be lower or higher than the performance data quoted  performance data does not reflect the deduction of the sales load or fee which if reflected would reduce the performance quoted  you will be charged a redemption fee equal to  of the net amount of the redemption if you redeem or exchange your shares  days or less after you purchase them portfolio characteristics as of june   inception date october   net assets  million total holdings  turnover ratio  investment style global equity market cap focus all cap minimum purchase  portfolio managers murray stahl chairman chief executive officer chief investment officer cofounder murray is chief executive officer chairman of the board of horizon kinetics and is a cofounder of the firm he has over thirty years of investing ex read more peter doyle managing director president of kinetics mutual funds inc cofounder peter is a managing director and cofounder of the firm  he is a senior member of the research team and a membe